    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "The Budget Act of 2025 made appropriations for the support of state government for the 2025\u201326 fiscal year.\n\nThis bill would amend the Budget Act of 2025 by amending items of appropriation.\n\nThis bill would declare that it is to take effect immediately as a Budget Bill."
    }
  ],
