    "impact_clause": "An act to amend the Budget Act of 2025 (Chapters 4 and 5 of the Statutes of 2025) by amending Items 0840-001-3268 and 4140-101-0001 of Section 2.00 of, and amending Sections 39.00 and 39.10 of, that act, relating to the state budget, and making an appropriation therefor, to take effect immediately, budget bill.",
